              </p>
            </li>
          </ol>

          In all four cases, we use <xref ref="T_propsofcong"></xref> to conclude that
          <m>ab \not \equiv 0 \pmod 3</m>.  For example, for the third case, we see that 
          <m>ab \equiv 2 \cdot 1 \pmod 3</m>.  That is, <m>ab \equiv 2 \pmod 3</m>.
        </p>
